des: Sunny 97 plays brighter music for a brighter day. Spiritual music to uplift your spirit and warm your soul. You can listen in East Idaho on your HD compatible radio at 97.3 HD3. Broadcasting to Pocatello, Blackfoot, Idaho Falls, Rigby, Rexburg and more.
